      "created_at": "2024-02-05T11:51:00.413Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi, I\u2019m not sure if this is already a thing, bit can you adjust the preset power level when pausing?</p>\n<p>So I\u2019m doing a hard workout and i need to pause for some reason, to answer the phone or because i want to puke because of acid build up, i hit pause and immediately the power setting is set to something low so that i can keep pedaling while finishing the phonecall or puke and continue my workout.</p>",
